data.description: Great Home on Big Lot! Featuring 3 Bedrooms, 2 Bathrooms, nestled on a cul-de-sac. Recently renovated with interior and exterior paint. Updated Kitchen includes all brand-new Stainless-Steel appliances and Quartz countertops. New carpet in bedrooms and updated bathrooms. Cozy Fireplace. Huge backyard with massive potential to create your own paradise. Peaceful neighborhood with no back neighbors. Conveniently located by 15 Freeway and the Mall of Victor Valley. Walking distance to Schools and Parks. Come take a look at this wonderful opportunity! Turnkey Home ready for your family!
